<p>
  The Department provides foreign language teaching to the bachelor's degree full-time and part-time students of all specialties of the university. During the first years of training university students study English, French or German languages for professional purpose.
</p>

<p>

  The Department teaching staff Languages trained at Surrey University (UK) and some leading universities of Ukraine, have experience in translation work and the preparation of English-language materials as part of IT soft TEAM project; as well as teaching English to military personnel - PEAF project; qualification Certificate in Teacher Training, Cambridge 1998 and Certificate of Proficiency in Test Design, Budapest 2000, etc.</p>
